text: Compsosoma nubilum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gounelle in 1908. It is known from Bolivia, Brazil and Paraguay.BioLib.cz - Compsosoma nubilum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1908
title: Compsosoma nubilum
